          <div class="craft-log reveal">
            <p class="craft-log-phase">Act I &nbsp;&#183;&nbsp; Phase One</p>
            <h3 class="craft-log-title">Before Video Generation</h3>
            <p class="craft-log-body">
              The video that jumpstarted the entire project. Images were AI-generated using ChatGPT, then character and scene elements were manually cut out using the Picsart mobile app. At the time, I was adapting Act I of <em>Tales of Solaria: Evin's Tale</em> — with the source document and a clear creative vision already in hand. Short clips were created and posted to TikTok (@Solarianearl), with the full scenes then compiled and uploaded to YouTube. The only editing tool used at this stage was InShot — for simple keyframing, cutouts, and transitions. The results weren't spectacular, but they brought the visuals to life. The final output came together as a slideshow for the Act I Prologue scene.
            </p>
            <div class="craft-log-links">
              <a href="https://youtu.be/6VELpAB69k4" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="craft-log-link">&#9654; Watch: Act I Prologue (Slideshow)</a>
