            </div>
            <p style="font-size:0.78rem; color:var(--color-text-faint); margin-top:var(--space-3); font-style:italic;">
              Note: A continuation of the Act I, Chapter 1 scene was also produced, ending on a deliberate cliffhanger. The intention was to produce more videos in this style, though limited tools and experience at the time made it difficult to take further.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Phase 2 -->
